<H3> <TI>   Residents Vote for Black Sea Fleet Base in Sevastopol </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Residents Vote for Black Sea Fleet Base in Sevastopol </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2806163994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1322 GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2806163994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondents] </F>
  [Text] Kiev 28 June TASS -- About 80 per cent of residents 
in the Crimean sea port of Sevastopol voted on Sunday for basing 
of the Russian Black Sea Fleet in their city, the press service 
of the Crimean Parliament told TASS on Tuesday. 
  The plebiscite was held on a par with the first round of 
Ukrainian presidential elections. 

</TEXT>

