<F P=102>   LD2806170094 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network in Kazakh 1400 GMT 
28 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2806170094 </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty Kazakh Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Kazakh </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A joint expanded sitting of the Supreme Kenges 
committees for economic reform and for finances and budget was 
held today. Members of the Cabinet of Ministers participated in 
its work. The program of the government was discussed. The 
program will be examined by the parliament and then endorsed by 
the president. The deputies paid attention to specific 
mechanisms for implementing some provisions of the program, 
especially in the field of credit and financial policy and 
