<H3> <TI>   Russian Peacekeepers Deploy Heavy Artillery in Abkhazia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Peacekeepers Deploy Heavy Artillery in Abkhazia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2806152394 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1000 GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2806152394 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi IBERIA </F>
<F P=105>  Georgian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Zugdidi, 28 Jun -- The Russian Federation 
peacekeeping forces have deployed heavy artillery (122mm-caliber 
E-30 howitzers) and heavy tanks (T-72 tanks) in the security 
zone of the Georgian- Abkhaz conflict. 
  No peacekeeping force, be it in former Yugoslavia or in 
Africa, is armed with either heavy artillery or heavy tanks 
since no such weaponry is necessary to carry out a peace mission. 

</TEXT>

