<F P=100> BALTIC STATES </F>
<F P=101> Estonia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Meri Appoints New Defense Minister </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Meri Appoints New Defense Minister </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2806144194 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network in Estonian 1400 
GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2806144194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network </F>
<F P=105>  Estonian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] President Lennart Meri today appointed Enn Tupp 
as defense minister. Enn Tupp is a member of the National 
Fatherland Party and has been working as the head of the Defense 
Ministry's defense policy department. [passage omitted] 
  President Lennart Meri released former defense minister 
Indrek Kannik from his post on 23 May. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

