<F P=106> [Unattributed report in the "Provincial Chronicle" column] </F>
  [Text] Kazan -- A program envisioning the restoration of 
the USSR on "a renewed organizational-legal basis" and the 
republic's accession to the Union has been adopted at the first 
congress of the Tatarstan Communist Party. The program notes 
that the Tataria leadership has managed to "cushion the blows by 
Russian authorities on the working people by supporting the 
agro-industrial complex, regulating prices, crime control, and 
targeted social protection programs." 

