  [Text] Kiev, 28 Jun -- A Cuban delegation led by Vice 
President of the Council of Ministers Lionel Soto was received 
by Supreme Council of Ukraine Chairman Oleksandr Moroz. He 
informed the delegation about the process of forming Ukraine's 
supreme legislative body and the decisions made to curb the 
economic crisis and to encourage nation-building in Ukraine. 
The meeting was attended by Ukrainian Foreign Minister Anatoliy 
