<F P=106> [Report by BELINFORM correspondent Svetlana Kalinkina for </F>
TASS] 
  [Text] Minsk 29 June TASS -- A Byelorussian [Belarusian] 
presidential election run-off will, most probably, be held on 
Sunday, 10 July. After numerous discussions, it is precisely 
