<H3> <TI>   Poll Shows Eastern Attitude Toward EU </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Poll Shows Eastern Attitude Toward EU </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU3005143594 Berlin NEUE ZEIT in German 27 May 94 pp 4-5 </F>
<F P=103> AU3005143594 </F>
