<H3> <TI>   Juppe: No Request for French Peacekeepers in Rwanda </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Juppe: No Request for French Peacekeepers in Rwanda </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2705142794 Paris Radio France International in French 1230 
GMT 27 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2705142794 </F>
