  [Text] The Council of Ministers has passed a major package 
of economic decrees which renews a number of expiring decrees, 
as well as introduces new regulations designed to streamline job 
placement, make direct recruitment easier, and provide fresh 
funds for Law 44, dealing with youth employment. 
